│ point. If computing common dominator is expensive, conservatively place the   │
│ broadcast in the function entry block. This guarantees dominance over all     │
│ uses in acyclic CFG. Example logic:\n  - Compute DominatorTree DT for the     │
│ function (already available in SLP).\n  - Collect BasicBlock* for all planned │
│ users of the new vector.\n  - BasicBlock* DomBB = findCommonDominator(DT,     │
